  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nThe `totalBlockValue` printed out when publish is wrong\r\n\r\n```\r\ninfo: Published block slot=7414120, validator=0x8955…5c2c, graffiti=Lodestar-v1.14.0/d7ca290, executionPayloadSource=engine, executionPayloadBlinded=false, executionPayloadValue=0.01908 ETH, consensusBlockValue=0.02732 ETH, totalBlockValue=27329242.01908 ETH, strictFeeRecipientCheck=false, builderSelection=executiononly, api=produceBlockV3\r\ninfo: Published block slot=7414416, validator=0x86c0…b87c, graffiti=Lodestar-v1.14.0/d7ca290, executionPayloadSource=engine, executionPayloadBlinded=false, executionPayloadValue=0.00628 ETH, consensusBlockValue=0.02464 ETH, totalBlockValue=24646563.00628 ETH, strictFeeRecipientCheck=false, builderSelection=executiononly, api=produceBlockV3\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe issue is likely related to https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/6286 as it looks like we missed to remove `gweiToWei` conversion.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/d7ca290d173dfa82b2977f3e94df6e5e8d12ef3e/packages/validator/src/services/block.ts#L225-L226\r\n\r\nBut it needs to be confirmed that this fixes the issue and if there are other places that need to be updated.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nShould print out correct total block value\r\n\r\n\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nProduce a block with `produceBlockV3` api\n\n### Additional context\n\n- https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/6286\n\n### Operating system\n\nLinux\n\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\n\nd7ca290d173dfa82b2977f3e94df6e5e8d12ef3e",
